Hi there! How can I assist you today?

few quaestion before i start! 
1) i need to upload the creatives first? 
2) where i can see the pixels?

Sure, I'd be happy to help with your questions! 
1) Yes, you will need to upload the creatives first. 
2) You can view and manage your pixels in the NewsBreak platform. If you need detailed instructions on how to install a NewsBreak Pixel with GTM, you can refer to this guide: [API Integration Guide](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/27680147056397-API-Integration-Guide).
where i go to upload the creatives?

To upload your creatives, you'll need to go to the Ad Creative section in your NewsBreak account. If you need more detailed guidance on best practices and A/B testing for your ad creatives, you can check out this article: [Ad Creative Best Practices and A/B Testing](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/20676690598029-Ad-Creative-Best-Practices-and-A-B-Testing).
in how much you reccomend to increase the budget?
It's recommended to increase your daily budget by 20-30% every 2-3 days. This gradual increase helps in maintaining the performance of your campaign without causing fluctuations.
